title: Tues Post Show (08-23-22)
itunes:title: Tues Post Show (08-23-22)
description:
Bobby talks about an interview he did with KTLA where they called him Bobby Jones. The life expectancy is dropping, Apple employees say they want to keep working at home and another scary incident on a plane. We also get into a discussion of lightyears and black holes. Eddie is thinking about growing out a mustache. We play the full interview that he did.
